Final POA — Oracle On-Prem to Oracle On-Prem Migration
===============================
1. Executive Summary
===============================

Objective:
Migrate Oracle 19c single-instance database DEVDB from existing on-premises server oraclelab1.localdomain.com to new target server oraclelab2.localdomain.com using RMAN Backup & Restore methodology.

Migration Type:
Oracle to Oracle (On-Prem to On-Prem)

Migration Goal:
Hardware refresh / infrastructure migration with minimal downtime and complete database integrity validation.

=================================
